{"product_id":"handwoven-chain-bracelet","title":"Handwoven Chain Bracelet","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis is an essential piece to adorn you day by day, on its own or combined with \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/luri.gold\/collections\/pendants\" title=\"charms\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"\u003echarms\u003c\/a\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe bracelet is made in 900 gold \u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e(21.6 karat), whose exceptional characteristics allow the metal wire to be bend and woven almost like fabric. It \u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eis crafted in the same, meditative technique used for thousands of years. The loop in loop chain may well be the oldest form of a chain and ancient peoples' goldsmiths, such as the Greek and Etruscans, produced intricate works with several strands and pendants with it.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis bracelet measures 18 cm in length, but can be made in any length, even as a necklace. Please \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/luri.gold\/pages\/contact\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"\u003econtact\u003c\/a\u003e me for any adjustments, together we will find your perfect fit.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eAs all LURI pieces, it is crafted entirely by hand.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"LURI jewels","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49297586585946,"sku":"","price":1900.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0885\/5217\/8010\/files\/DSC1535_646330a2-3e8f-453f-af7c-d0e5d22eb2e3.jpg?v=1723562559","url":"https:\/\/luri.gold\/products\/handwoven-chain-bracelet","provider":"LURI jewels","version":"1.0","type":"link"}